<body>
<div><head>《東宮舊事》</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-1a.2">皇太子初拜，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-1a.3">有旄幢一。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-1a.4">又曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-1a.5">皇太子鹵簿有黃麾。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-1a.6">皇太子初拜，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-1a.7">有石山安車一、建九旗青色四馬。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-1a.8">又曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-1a.9">皇太子大小會庭設三廂，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-1a.10">樂舞六佾。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-2a.2">皇太子納妃，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-2a.3">有漆龍頭支髻枕一、銀花鐶鈕自副。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-2a.4">又曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-2a.5">皇太子納妃，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-2a.6">有金塗連盤鴨燈一。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-2a.7">太子納妃，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-2a.8">有絳地文履一量。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-2a.9">又曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-2a.10">皇太子納妃有漆花簏二具。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-3a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-3a" ed="CHANT" n="001-3a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-3a.2">皇太子納妃，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-3a.3">織成衮帶白玉珮。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-3a.4">皇太子納妃，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-3a.5">四望車羽葆前後部鼓吹各一部，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-3a.6">又曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-3a.7">步搖一具九鈿函盛之。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-3a.8">太子有銅駞頭燈銅倚燈，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-3a.9">納妃有金塗四尺長燈、銀塗二尺連盤燈。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-4a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-4a" ed="CHANT" n="001-4a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-4a.2">太子納妃，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-4a.3">有縠白紗、白絹衫並紫結纓。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-4a.4">皇太子納妃，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-4a.5">有絳紗複裙、絳碧結綾複裙、丹碧紗紋雙裙、紫碧紗文雙裙、紫碧紗文繡纓雙裙、紫碧紗縠雙裙、丹碧杯文羅裙。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-4a.6">皇太子初拜，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-4a.7">給縹紅𥿄各一百枚。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-5a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-5a" ed="CHANT" n="001-5a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-5a.2">皇太子初拜，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-5a.3">給香墨四丸。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-5a.4">太子儀餙有玉頭劍。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-5a.5">閣內有曲鄣，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-5a.6">鄣上崔目窗。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-6a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-6a" ed="CHANT" n="001-6a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-6a.2">太子納妃，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-6a.3">有玳瑁鈿鏤鏡臺一。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-6a.4">太子納妃，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-6a.5">有龍頭金縷交刀四、銀牙鏁綵帶副二。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-6a.6">皇太子初拜，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-6a.7">有絳紗單衣。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-7a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-7a" ed="CHANT" n="001-7a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-7a.2">漆四升杯四十、漆杯子三百。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-7a.3">長槃五、漆尺槃三千、漆柏灸桿二。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-7a.4">漆三十五、子方樏二、杳蓋二枚。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-7a.5">白珥五枝。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-8a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-8a" ed="CHANT" n="001-8a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-8a.2">漆盌子一百枚。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-8a.3">漆匕五十枚。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-8a.4">漆箸一百雙。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-8a.5">漆貊灸大函一具。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-9a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-9a" ed="CHANT" n="001-9a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-9a.2">漆注綺織筥一十枚。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-9a.3">漆食架二。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-9a.4">太子妃有石砧一枚，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-9a.5">又擣衣砧杵十枚。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-9a.6">皇太子納妃，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-9a.7">自著衣大鏡尺八寸、銀花小鏡尺二寸、漆匣盛翡翠銅鏡二枚、嵌金龍頭受福蓮華鉤鏁四副。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-10a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-10a" ed="CHANT" n="001-10a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-10a.2">皇太子納妃，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-10a.3">有綠石綺絹裏床幨二。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-10a.4">太子納妃，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-10a.5">有青布碧裡梁下幃一，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-10a.6">絣絹青布窗戶幃各一。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-10a.7">太子納妃，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-10a.8">有綵杯文綺被一、絳具文羅一幅，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-10a.9">一絳被羅，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-10a.10">綉文四五幅，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-10a.11">被一，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-10a.12">又有七綵文綺被，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-10a.13">絳文羅面一<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-11a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-11a" ed="CHANT" n="001-11a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-11a.2">太子納妃，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-11a.3">有赤花雙文簞。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-11a.4">太子有獨坐龍鬚蓆赤皮花經席一領。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-11a.5">皇太子納妃，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-11a.6">有床上屏風十二、牒織成漆連銀鉤鈕織成連地屏風十四、牒銅環鈕。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-12a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-12a" ed="CHANT" n="001-12a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-12a.2">皇太子初拜，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-12a.3">供漆要扇青竹扇各一、納妃同心扇二十、單竹扇二十。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-12a.4">太子有白毦拂二。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-12a.5">太子納妃，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-12a.6">有漆書銀帶唾壺一。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-13a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-13a" ed="CHANT" n="001-13a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-13a.2">皇太子初拜，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-13a.3">有銅慱山香爐一枚，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-13a.4">納妃。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-13a.5">泰元中，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-13a.6">皇太子納妃王氏，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-13a.7">有銀塗慱山蓮槃三十、香爐一。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-13a.8">皇太子納妃，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-13a.9">有綾裏幞帊五具、絹裏幞帊五具。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-14a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-14a" ed="CHANT" n="001-14a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-14a.2">皇太子初拜，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-14a.3">有漆馬齒書簏、金裝彩花簏。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-14a.4">皇太子納妃，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-14a.5">有絳直文羅袴七、彩杯文錦袴五。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-14a.6">皇太子納妃，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-14a.7">有絳紗複裙、絳碧結綾妖裙、丹碧紗紋雙裙、紫碧紗紋雙裙、紫碧紗紋綉纓雙裙、紫碧縠紗縠雙裙、丹碧杯文雙裙。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-15a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-15a" ed="CHANT" n="001-15a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-15a.2">太子納妃，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-15a.3">有絳地紋履一雙。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-15a.4">皇太子初拜，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-15a.5">給漆筆四十枚、銅慱山筆床一副。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-15a.6">太子納妃，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1368_CHANT_001-15a.7">有絳綾袍一領。<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
